<app cb:word-count="46" from="#beg0215003" to="#end0215003"><lem wit="#wit1"><note place="inline">當作高貴鄉公六年。蓋齊王芳立十五年而廢矣。正宗記云。寶林傳誤作己卯。當是齊王芳丁卯歲也。然<lb n="0215a23" ed="T"/>則乃是八年也</note></lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0215004" to="#end0215004"><lem wit="#wit1">其</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">別</rdg></app>
<app from="#beg0215005" to="#end0215005"><lem wit="#wit1">即</lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2">既</rdg></app>
<app cb:word-count="34" from="#beg0216001" to="#end0216001"><lem wit="#wit1"><note place="inline">正宗記云。宋孝武之世也。<lb n="0216b21" ed="T"/>又注云。以達磨六十七年算之。當在宋孝武建元元年甲午也</note></lem><rdg resp="#resp1" wit="#wit2"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
</p>
