<note n="0211002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0211002">〔正宗云與次子〕－【明】</note>
<note n="0211003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0211003">〔與〕－【明】</note>
<note n="0211004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0211004">我故＝故我【明】</note>
